description: Recently sold: $405,000. 6178 Boulderbelle Rd is a beautiful 3 bed, 2 bath home on 12 acres in Saginaw! Bright and spacious, this home has it all! Huge updated kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Big sliding glass doors in the living room bring in tons of natural light. A wood-burning stove in the dining room offers extra warmth and coziness in the winter. The Master Bedroom has a walk-in closet and an attached full master bath with 2 sinks. Main floor laundry. Tons of fresh paint throughout, as well as new flooring (carpet, tile) in much of the house. And if that wasn't enough, there is also a 6 car garage that is full of extra space! In addition to plenty of parking and storage, the heated and insulated garage boasts a huge office area! One big open room with three smaller rooms attached make for a great home office. This space also has a sink and in-floor heat, as well as a laundry sink and washtub for pets. Pet lover's personal pet grooming room outfitted with wash tub for small and big dogs. Groomers table, in wall vacuum and Maytag washer and dryer for pet towels. Outside, enjoy the landscaped yard and a deck off of the kitchen. Or roam your 12 acres of land! Additional 15 acres is available as well. This home is a must-see. Schedule your showing today!

description: Recently sold: $206,000. This beautiful 3+++ bedroom, 2 full bathroom home is truly one of a kind. Located on 1 acre with beautiful yard is within 1 mile of Grand Lakes public access point, and close to Caribou Lake. The main floor boasts with a large kitchen, lots of natural light, high ceilings throughout, and wood floors. Main floor laundry, office space, and extra room currently being used as a nursery. description:
Recently sold: $250,000. This wonderful home, sitting on 7 beautiful acres, offers spacious country living without the long commute! The home has 2 living rooms, an eat-in kitchen, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms (one of which has a jetted tub), and abundant natural light both upstairs and down.  The home is all electric with forced air heat that uses a high-efficiency, off-peak heating system that keeps costs down.  A new septic system was installed in 2015 and is fully-compliant. 

The upper deck, which runs the entire south side of the house, offers great views of the property, and a portion of it is enclosed to allow for 3-season use.  There is a 2-car attached garage, garden shed, carport, chicken coop, and fenced in veggie garden on the property.  Lots of space in the driveway accommodates large family functions, and the yard has over 2 acres of in-ground fencing installed and ready to keep your pets safe with hookup of a transmitter.

This FSBO home really has it all!!

Call (202) 607-5426 today for a showing!

description: Recently sold: $140,000. Great Ranch style home in Saginaw! Sitting on approximately 4 acres, this 2+ bedroom 1 bath home offers many great features! Make sure to come take a look before it's gone!

description: Recently sold: $207,900. Enjoy country living at 5912 Glacier Trail! This 3 bed, 2 bath home in Saginaw sits on nearly 10 acres of beautifully wooded land that has the Beaver River flowing through it. Located between Fish Lake and the Cloquet River on a secluded and private road, adjacent to thousands of acres of state land, and only minutes from public access on Fish Lake. The home has lots of windows to let in natural light, and a wood burning fireplace in the large downstairs family room. Cork flooring in the downstairs bedroom. Detached 4-car garage.

description:
Recently sold: $325,000. LAKE HOME LIVING! This 3 bedroom home sits, literally, on the shores of Big Grand Lake which is an amazingly easy proximity to Duluth and all areas! Situated close to the Lake Shore this property has so much to offer besides the year-round tranquil views....enjoy water sports just a stones throw from your deck, fish off your dock, or just sit in peace in the living/dining room while looking out at the majestic west facing views with breathtaking sunsets! An open living room/dining and kitchen provide a practical floor plan for lake living! One level convenience with a main floor laundry, attached garage, main floor master suite & 2 other bedrooms for guests & kids! Walk out to an adorable year-round log cabin with lofted sleeping quarters and gas stove!  Parking for everyone, shed storage AND a lofted studio building complete with heated game room/studio and sleeping quarters! Plus...additional garage, covered storage space, lower level exercise area and upper balcony!! Don't miss the Raspberries, Blueberries, Grapes, Apple trees and Plum trees! The entire "RETREAT" is a well maintained piece of the lake that would be a special place to gather & enjoy for YOUR FAMILY & FRIENDS!
- Efficient Dual Fuel Heating (Electric Baseboard & Gas Fireplace & Stoves)
- Level Lot , Home right on the waters edge
- Open Floor Plan
- Updated Kitchen Appliances , quartz countertops
- Master Bedroom with 3/4 bath en suite
- 2013 New Septic System
- Log Cabin w/ Sleeping Loft & Gas Stove Heat
- Studio Building/1 Car Garage w/ Rec Area & Gym / Storage
- Ample Parking Space
